{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Boss Breaker is a twin-stick beat 'em up set within the Nexus Orion Labs corporate compound. You were hired as a product tester for the all-new &quot;Breaker Fists,&quot; but after a chance encounter and a paperwork mixup, you'll have to unravel the secrets of your employer and take them down once and for all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras/cropped-fight-2.gif?t=1730396633\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">MORE THAN MEETS THE EYE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Vending machines do far more for you than give you snacks - they give you powerful upgrades for your fists and allow you to further your capabilities. These high-tech dispensers fall from the ceiling every once in a while, so make sure to use them when you can! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras/shop-bb-unscale.gif?t=1730396633\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">HIGH TREASON</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Any dissent is immediately silenced, and anyone caught spreading it is never seen again. The entire company is against you, so do you have what it takes to take it down without being annihilated first?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras/cropped-fight-6.gif?t=1730396633\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PICK UP AND PLAY HOW YOU WANT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Designed to be picked up and played right away, Boss Breaker allows you to ignore the story completely if you want, instead opting to focus on destroying everything in your path. If that's not your style, stick around and uncover the secret history of Nexus Orion Labs. No matter how you play, we have you covered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/extras/cropped-fight-4.gif?t=1730396633\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Basic Training","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2869030/d5d9cb68c281d2bd1689b327b7138630bb1afc56.jpg"},{"name":"Master Archivist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2869030/91fa122237cb408f1989502ab7a12c4564f110d3.jpg"},{"name":"Bit The Dust","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2869030/ca527f7de37fb267c5ae54e73a8bd92b28a2b5ee.jpg"},{"name":"Overthrown","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2869030/80097096f4a816c1f0631c0ee84911fef2970dc3.jpg"},{"name":"Security Bypass","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2869030/a5f65e3323d7aba3d73cac13d06f53ad3ec3b267.jpg"},{"name":"Forgotten Truth","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2869030/a37ef8b5e1f1927219eb019c2a9e391dd3fed313.jpg"},{"name":"Right Back At Ya'","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2869030/de8626ee17e450c3a1836474887e778311a46fe0.jpg"},{"name":"1 in 1000","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2869030/f780ef0e2417639124c7314f482160c88252f389.jpg"},{"name":"Resignation","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2869030/9abca6e7bc3b070758e02f6e3ce000f0543470a1.jpg"},{"name":"All The Connections","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2869030/81293d7e90ac79c162c17cf0ccb7052d33a9438b.jpg"}],"total":14},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869030/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730396633","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/stor